    "ConfidentiallyThe patient EMR is kept encrypted in a document-oriented database.",
    "The hash value of the data are kept on the blockchain.",
    "In this way, any change on the data can be easily detected and patient confidentiality is protected.",
    "Smart contracts are used to prevent malicious access and provide secure access to data.",
    "IntegrityThe use of a blockchain in the proposed scheme prevents data from being modified by undesired manipulations."
